latestPosts.caption:
At HANNAN’s core lies our ever growing love and obsession with gemstones, these candies of nature that continue to leave me in awe every time they’re in my hands. We’re so grateful to have our tiny factory of the best peeps in Jaipur that carve, polish and cut these otherworldly gems into the stories that make HANNAN. 

It was our precious associations with retailers across Japan early on in our journey that helped out take our quality and precision to new heights. We’re nowhere close to perfect but appreciate the love and patience as we strive to make everyday better than yesterday.
